Fodor and the Six Hundred Hungarians
According to the Minister of Environment and Hydrology G<0xC3><0xA1>bor Fodor, the expert-level meetings will end on Tuesday and Wednesday after the official inauguration will continue the minister-level negotiations on the international climate regime after 2012.
